      <title>花旗表示，印度流动性舒适标志着宽松周期的开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/india-liquidity-comfort-signals-start-of-easing-cycle-citi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团表示，印度银行流动性的改善已推动主要隔夜利率在五个月的差距后向政策利率走低，这标志着印度货币政策宽松的开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/india-liquidity-comfort-signals-start-of-easing-cycle-citi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 06:22:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着风暴加强，另外两场旋风可能袭击澳大利亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/two-more-cyclones-likely-to-hit-australia-as-storms-strengthen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚北部海岸附近形成的两场风暴可能会在周末成为热带气旋，这是今年袭击该大陆的一系列风暴中的最新一场——破坏基础设施并损害农作物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/two-more-cyclones-likely-to-hit-australia-as-storms-strengthen</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 06:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
